                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/8278" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">CSR-0237</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1645 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">客户至上？业绩至上？总经理的商业伦理决策难题</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Customer First? Performance First? The Business Ethics Decision-making Dilemma of General Manager</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">赵少琼，李慧</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中国石油大学（北京）</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">北京掌凡科技公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">服务业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">13 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">伦理决策；利益相关者；企业责任竞争力</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Ethical decision-making, stakeholders, corporate responsibility competitiveness</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本文讲述了北京掌凡科技公司的K事业部总经理在面对外部竞争压力日益增大，内部组织架构频繁变革和调整的情景下，为完成CEO的绩效考核目标，而深入一线寻找销售额不稳定的症结。在此过程中，事业部内产品和销售之间的矛盾逐渐显露出来，总经理也面临“追求个人短期利益最大化”或“客户至上，维护客户信任”的两难选择，作为企业高管决策的典型案例，希望借助该案例，真实还原企业高管在面临社会责任冲突时的决策情景，让学习者身临其境，体验商业伦理和社会责任的魅力。
通过描述总经理与个人、团队、企业和客户多方权益博弈的过程，旨在启发学习者对企业社会责任、伦理决策的过程与企业责任竞争力模型等理论的深入思考和学习，以便学习者后续在经营决策中做出正确的商业伦理选择。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">This paper describes the Beijing Zhangfan Technology Company K business division general manager in the face of increasing external pressure of competition, the internal organizational structure of frequent change and adjustment of the scenario, in order to complete the CEO&#39;s performance assessment objectives, and into the front line to find the crux of the unstable sales.In this process, the contradictions between the product and sales in the division gradually emerged, the general manager is also facing the &quot;pursuit of personal short-term interests maximization&quot; or &quot;customer first, maintain customer trust&quot; dilemma choice, as a typical case of enterprise executive decision-making, hope with the help of the case, the real reduction of enterprise executives in the face of social responsibility conflict decision-making scenario, so that learners immerse themselves in the scene, experience the charm of business ethics and social responsibility.Through the description of the general manager and individuals, teams, enterprises and customers multi-party rights and interests of the game process, aims to inspire learners to corporate social responsibility, ethical decision-making process and corporate responsibility competitiveness model of theory in-depth thinking and learning, so that learners follow-up in business decisions to make the right choice of business ethics.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《商业伦理与企业社会责任》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">利益相关者;社会责任金字塔理论;企业责任竞争力模型;企业社会责任观</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024-04</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
